-- Cablevision Said Near Purchase of Bresnan Communications for $1.3 Billion
-- Sylvia Wier
-- 2010-06-13T17:27:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/cablevision-said-near-purchase-of-bresnan-communications-for-1-3-billion.html

          
          
             Cablevision Systems Corp. is said to
be near the purchase of Bresnan Communications for about $1.3
billion, people close to the negotiations said.  
          
          


  
     
       
     
           
                            
                     
                     Acquiring Bresnan would give Cablevision a bigger slice of the burgeoning market for high-speed Internet services. Photographer: Rick Maiman/Bloomberg  
                           

     
